cu.explanation_en: Changing Num_Threads_PUSCH from integer 8 to string "eight" will cause type validation failure in configuration parsing, leading to system initialization errors.

du.explanation_en: Setting tr_n_preference to an invalid enum 'invalid' will cause configuration validation failure, preventing proper F1 interface setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 tr_n_preference 設定為無效的枚舉值 'invalid' 會導致配置驗證失敗，阻止正確的 F1 介面設定。
